reviewText: Great information to get you over the hump on those cold chilly days. Love the information she shares.

Dara is so real and relaxed in the kitchen. She makes shifting to a radically new lifestyle completely approachable. And her happy personality makes you want to know her (I wish I did!) I have absolute certainty that if you follow her way of eating and drinking, you will be healthier than you were before. No doubt!!

I also appreciate the production values on Dara's DVDs, which is really important to me as a professional video editor and producer.
A good DVD to get started on a raw living lifestyle but I would recommend also buying Dara's tonics DVD also

I'm a big fan Of Ms. Dubinet and I've followed over the years, however these DVD's!~ she really outdid herself on so many levels. The quality of the DVD's and level of information and entertainment was absolutely perfect. I would suggest this video for anyone at any age or sex to check this out and how tasty and healing healthy food can be.
